text: Of þære ea in to Wulfstanes fleote, of Wulfstanes fleote andlang dices on hokes clif, of hokes clive andlang mærces on Snelles pitte, of Snelles pitte andlang mærke on Hafokes boerh, of Hafokes beorhge on þonne wyte wege, on þæet sclæde, of þam sclæde on Echilde hlæwe a þa smye wicce, of Echilde hlæwe on hengstes earas of hengstes earas on litil healle andlang mearke on Warmundes stan, of Warmundes stan on Foxslades eande, of Foxslades ænde on þære hole wege of þære hole wege to Kynewirdtreow, of Kynewirdtreow andlang mærke on Howille, of Howille in to þære ea.
